  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e010bc8b-aeb1-48ef-aed8-f81799709d83\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ffcc209-9748-4f0d-833f-2015a850be91\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bf1a7cdf-7b3b-4845-982d-80ad366f50b0\">목~어깨 사이의 통증 말고,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-05deb648-dd74-4002-8117-74abbeac296d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fb24bd0c-46a5-4d17-afba-fadaeb7006c7\">어깨 관절 부위가 아픈 경우입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d4463b32-f791-49cb-80a8-c33ee060c8e2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97a963a9-f8a6-46b8-aa26-77a43853481b\">젊은 분들은 운동 손상 또는 외상에 의한 경우가 많고,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3adfebac-75cd-4e8c-a772-24d499aa1f9b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f3470d65-4e55-4624-a2da-09cb9f3ff10d\">40세를 넘어가는 중장년층에는 노화로 인해 힘줄과 관절이 약해지면서 이유 없이 발생하기도 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-06ba69a0-9274-4946-a1f3-318cf2a82545\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0c1fa6f7-0f1c-4395-929f-85c995dc298a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-de6efad5-8e20-4dae-9205-581a3f415948\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-01eb7881-6967-4f35-bbae-f4a8f1e02a70\">아래 그림을 보시죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb7ca8ec-b1cd-4063-bea9-483aa93a345d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cab52560-cd10-486b-a7b2-ebd909577b3b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e1343eee-f877-49c8-b3cf-67ea68df6038\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e1343eee-f877-49c8-b3cf-67ea68df6038\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2722a5db70ebdcfb.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1527\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2722a5db70ebdcfb.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2722a5db70ebdcfb.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e24d1b99-69e8-4a9f-8e45-d8204eb01130\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-77e9a96e-fc9a-4d3e-abe1-aa1b4f26cc5f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-de68e611-aa0f-4f2d-9483-00b4dce2ca72\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dd8e0b2e-009c-4a1c-b736-2749df4f21df\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-94614f65-1a84-4d18-b1de-bf3800e792ef\">평소에 어깨 관절의 유연성을 유지하면서 가동 범위를 늘리기 위한 관리를 해주면 치료 및 예방에 도움이 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0610dfd0-4b0b-44d1-bbcf-d1dd057dbd0f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1460ef15-4e8b-43c9-b7cf-b18f4d1f5d72\">아래 그림을 보고 할 수 있는 동작은 따라 해보세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba22fd15-54bb-4248-846c-22985f69454e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ba22fd15-54bb-4248-846c-22985f69454e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/94d01d10693c0d26.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1527\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/94d01d10693c0d26.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/94d01d10693c0d26.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eca6dd2c-4d4a-4607-a8aa-a8f7a3571389\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f469baa1-1ec3-4795-8b18-e9cb68dfd80a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-30d65ff1-8ed2-4085-abd5-b33c67893419\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0c284c90-96c5-4043-a11f-fddf92156728\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e8da60a3-ed1a-4b4b-9800-83d202c01aca\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9505e246-3f5b-4a4d-9c20-c7546df2da5b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0351141b-77fa-447f-9652-6326ff480279\">누구나 한 번은 무릎 통증을 경험합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-884eed9f-43dc-4ce6-b3ef-09ba9f50409b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-90c1b3ab-205e-4a4f-9e8f-659f23c81eb7\">젊어서는 오래 걷기, 달리기, 등산, 안 좋은 자세 등으로 인해 일시적으로 무릎 통증을 경험하지만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1486ea02-7ba9-404f-bac2-26d2a41ecb9e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c7ab9906-ad64-415e-94d1-43bd2b2c0702\">역시나 나이가 들면서 연골의 퇴행 및 힘줄과 인대의 약화로 인해 반복적이고 만성적인 무릎 통증을 경험하기 시작합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a16f3b7-5521-4b7f-a43e-930487d82faf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e7e74d2a-50bd-44cb-a964-4013b46caffa\">50세가 넘어서 무릎이 아프기 시작하면 덜컥 겁부터 나죠. &#x27;무릎 관절염이 이제 시작되는 건가? 나중에 인공관절 수술해야 하면 어떻게 하지?&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d9df3455-3044-4356-bf23-d84f53e99de5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a7a0fbb-a1f1-401d-ab6b-c37908292143\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-21d4ba97-d206-417e-97e9-24cd980a6af6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-55bdf2ec-e750-4383-90b5-9e747d8d164d\">다리 근육(특히 허벅지 &amp; 엉덩이)을 강화하고 체중을 조절하면서 관절에 무리가 가는 활동은 줄이는 게 좋습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-095ee725-994f-4e15-a403-dd33891cbea0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8b180b79-bc6a-411a-b9f8-61a3ace3e806\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af214742-8957-40db-9b9c-fb39f3246066\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-af214742-8957-40db-9b9c-fb39f3246066\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a181533e4216732.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1527\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a181533e4216732.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a181533e4216732.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d79456e7-5651-49a6-be60-878909327a56\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f4ee60ea-34e2-4a40-89fe-f40ff464fec7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3c901833-f390-43b3-a13a-4b45092d21b5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7811ff61-f38b-480b-b401-2936b1d5a4f4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e3e7f234-9687-447a-a98f-381f8e8be1ae\">무릎 통증을 예방하고 무릎 관절을 아끼려면 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-89d413ce-5a6d-445e-9407-4fc5323cbdeb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ea8912ae-1aa2-43c5-8248-30774e002d9d\">스트레칭도 중요하지만, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cbde8a2d-a140-449c-846d-71c19318cad5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d4ed023a-a53c-4db4-ab62-7194bb05d0eb\">역시나 근육의 강화가 중요합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e138e54-48b1-4c86-9f8e-aa3ead021c60\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1060593f-4202-4f93-8b86-ea50529c8d18\">아래 그림을 보시고 따라 할 수 있는 동작은 따라 해보세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84498f1f-eede-4379-8d0d-edec48b69e21\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-efaf6d0e-eefc-436d-9edc-44fa3c1d7235\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-38fe8c91-a43f-4a56-aec8-0f314e2d6f5b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-38fe8c91-a43f-4a56-aec8-0f314e2d6f5b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d28546b0c43b3d0e.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1527\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d28546b0c43b3d0e.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d28546b0c43b3d0e.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ade4bc4c-ebc0-4fab-92cc-6a1c76cd95f6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9fa6ec76-8e0f-492c-b214-c1f43d736838\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-08242d7b-a6bf-47c1-9979-8d3bf8475949\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b7f63b4-ea7f-4e8c-a5d2-d27f4d656967\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-07edd5a1-641f-4364-8a03-efa5ea27b679\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7d662c9-77be-4347-9b0f-6d0ba423da93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9b3d0581-ce7d-4751-9985-70dfd6c6702f\">전체 인구의 절반 이상이 허리 통증을 경험하고 허리 통증으로 고생한다고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dc150584-ee31-4c81-98a3-753cb690a568\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81978eea-c552-48ee-8d46-07fc5e4cf13f\">요통환자의 10%는 만성 요통에 시달린다고 하구요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8554489c-50a2-4e21-88fd-4e31c97e9cbe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ed12d895-676c-48b9-88fc-c6b74ec36802\">한국의 5천만 인구 중 2천5백만 명은 허리가 아파본 경험이 있고, 그 중 10%인 2백5십만 명은 만성 요통에 시달린다니.. 정말 많은 사람이 허리 통증으로 고생하고 있네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-01659ff8-45c5-4e48-af99-876b1f733171\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-47391ddb-eb07-42ca-ae89-47bed3532a8f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7752b88d-7838-4836-988f-09fe0d8806db\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7752b88d-7838-4836-988f-09fe0d8806db\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5b8e68de48d1fd36.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1526\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5b8e68de48d1fd36.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5b8e68de48d1fd36.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-01faa261-5e91-470c-b555-25a23d329aaa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <d